          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>In Tableau, the story consists of four scenes. Each scene represents a unique visualization created during the analysis. These scenes guide the user step-by-step through budget allocation insights, including category-wise, department-wise, scheme-wise analysis and overall budget overview.</run>
